rComments: Professor Kim's lectures rely heavily on class discussion and student presentations, but unlike many professors who follow this format, she manages to make them entertaining and engaging. She usually had a line of students waiting to talk to her afterwards, and would always chat with anyone for as long as they wished. Sweet person, and great class.

Great professor, her lectures are always very organized and interesting. Explains concepts very clearly, and always very approachable if you have any questions. As long as you attend the lectures, keep up with the weekly online assignments, this course is an easy A. Highly recommended bird course, especially if you're into learning languages.

Such a caring and genuine lady. Cares so much about her students and her course. If you work hard and participate she will award you with a great mark as she is a very fair instructor. Awesome teacher and person.

Hang-Sun Kim is a great professor! She's extremely kind & very easy to approach. She's also a fair marker. I really enjoyed the material of the seminar and would recommend everyone to take CCR199 - Cities, Real & Imagined.
Frau Kim was an amazing teacher for first year German. Really enjoyable and she knew what she was doing.
I intend to take as many classes as I can with her.  Inspirational prof, very open to speaking with students after class or during her office hours.
